{"tid":2063951,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［置頂討論］國際線 - Twitter版十點鳩叫 ！！！","createTime":"2020-06-14T12:09:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T13:30:21.000Z","uid":194164,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"68b0223053c56a3d541fbfc0767d925eb022954f","tid":2063951,"uid":194164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T12:09:27.000Z","msg":"其實好似10點鳩叫咁 每晚2130-2200都全部人上twitter 目標global trend 一兩個hashtag有無得唸？ <br />\n<br />\n如果支持(真係會幫手做既）可唔可以👍🏼 <br />\n多人肯做會嘗試策劃個daily twitter trend campaign <br />\n<br />\n<strong>每日主推一個hashtag</strong><br />\n唔一定係好香港specify好似 <span style=\"color: orange;\">#HongKongProtests #FightForFreedom #StandwithHongKong</span> <br />\n有時可以做generic啲同全世界connect例如<span style=\"color: orange;\"> #PoliceBrutality #WomensRight #ChildAbuse </span><br />\n甚至乎主打CCP好似 <span style=\"color: orange;\">#CCP_is_terrorist #CCPVirus #BoycottMadeInChina</span><br />\n<br />\n如果一個hashtag上worldwide trend係會多好人留意<br />\n夜晚時間歐美亞洲都起晒身 audience reach會最多<br />\n<br />\n<strong>初步構思 </strong><br />\n1.每日lunch hour公布一個hashtag (大家可以隨時開始）<br />\n2. 大家各自係選擇相應既 相片/影片/文宣<br />\n3. 配上外語caption (如果中文 - 用書面語) <br />\n4. 加daily hashtag (可以追加其他#)<br />\n5. 盡量like晒其他手足既post務求將香港人既post推高 reach多啲外人<br />\n&mdash;&gt; 有寫得好既post就幫手Retweet埋、comment加把嘴<br />\n等佢可以再推高啲<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家一齊brainstorm <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">#國際係 #手足互科 #日常抗爭</span>"},{"pid":"6268a9f9ce237ef0657023553ec62bb3fcf95be4","tid":2063951,"uid":82815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T12:15:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a10b06dc68302f366dce51cb3d023b1ea6a2dc","tid":2063951,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T12:18:41.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"aa9eaa03632eb5fd2e854aa2656b6e783528719e","tid":2063951,"uid":242393,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"r